		 Month: May 2012 			  The Universal Campus  	 
		  
  Pierre Baldi  and  Cristina Videira Lopes  have developed an infrastructure called the  Universal Campus which allows, among other things, the organization and deployment of scientific meeting, conferences, classes, etc in a 3D virtual world. 2011. The work has been published in the  ACM ELearn magazine . 
	 

